  'moqueta-las-vegas-poliamida',
  '<p><img width="800" height="600" src="https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1024x768.jpeg" alt="Moqueta Las Vegas Azul" srcset="https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-180x135.jpeg 180w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-640x480.jpeg 640w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1366x1025.jpeg 1366w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1600x1200.jpeg 1600w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-1920x1440.jpeg 1920w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46-600x450.jpeg 600w, https://www.disstands.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-27-at-10.41.46.jpeg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" />															</p>
<h1>Moqueta Las Vegas: La Solución Premium 100% Poliamida para Eventos Profesionales</h1>
